 usually best to build without them once and then run
-\verb+ldd+\footnote{\verb+otool+ on OSX and \verb+depends.exe+ on Windows}
+\verb+ldd+\footnote{\texttt{otool} on OSX and \texttt{depends.exe} on Windows}
